<QuestionForm xmlns="http://mechanicalturk.amazonaws.com/AWSMechanicalTurkDataSchemas/2005-10-01/QuestionForm.xsd">
  <Overview>
    <Title>Scraper Qualification</Title>
    <Text>
      This qualification requires use of Scraper extension on the Google Chrome browser. The Qualification tests that you have installed the Scraper and know how to use it.
    </Text>
  </Overview>
