    <QuestionIdentifier>xpath</QuestionIdentifier>
    <QuestionContent>
      <FormattedContent><![CDATA[
            <h1>1. Installing the Scraper extension</h1>
            <p>
                Go to the <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/mbigbapnjcgaffohmbkdlecaccepngjd?hc=search&hcp=main">scraper installation page</a>. Install the Scraper extension by clicking on the 'Add to Chrome' button, then clicking 'Install'.</p>
            <img src="http://ec2-50-18-19-3.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com:8080/qualification/img/install2-1.png" alt="Adding scraper to Chrome" width="525" height="330" />
            <p>
                If the installation is successful, or if you already have the extension installed,
                the button should instead say "Added to Chrome".</p>
            <img src="http://ec2-50-18-19-3.us-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com:8080/qualification/img/install3.png" alt="scraper added!" width="525" height="330" />
            <p>
                Now that you've installed the Scraper, learn how to use it!!
            </p>
